msgid "SETTINGS_AUTO_RECONNECT_WIIMOTE"
msgstr "Reconectar Mando de Wii Automáticamente"

msgid "SETTINGS_AUTO_RECONNECT_WIIMOTE_DESCRIPTION"
msgstr "Luego de haber conectado un mando de Wii, se reconectará automáticamente la mayor parte del tiempo."

msgid "SETTINGS_CLASSIC_SOUNDS"
msgstr "Sonidos Clásicos de Botones"

msgid "SETTINGS_CLASSIC_SOUNDS_DESCRIPTION"
msgstr "Al estar activado, se utilizarán los efectos de sonido originales de Flipnote Studio en lugar de sus versiones de Flipnote Organizer."

msgid "SETTINGS_CLEAR_FLIPNOTE_CACHE"
msgstr "Limpiar Caché de Flipnotes"

msgid "SETTINGS_FLIPNOTE_DETAILS_DIGITAL_SHIFT"
msgstr "Tecla Shift Digital"

msgid "SETTINGS_FLIPNOTE_DETAILS_DIGITAL_SHIFT_DESCRIPTION"
msgstr "Para cuando la tecla Shift no se encuentre disponible, o en caso de que sea preferible que la tecla se mantenga presionada. Esta opción no se puede utilizar si el Modo Galería está activado."

msgid "SETTINGS_FLIPNOTE_DETAILS_SHIFT"
msgstr "Detalles Extra al Presionar Shift"

msgid "SETTINGS_FLIPNOTE_DETAILS_SHIFT_DESCRIPTION"
msgstr "Al pulsar Shift o la Tecla Digital Shift, se mostrarán detalles extra de los Flipnotes. Se recomienda mantener esta opción activada. Esta opción no se puede utilizar si el Modo Galería está activado."

msgid "SETTINGS_FLIPNOTE_PLAYER_VOLUME"
msgstr "Volumen del Reproductor de Flipnotes"

msgid "SETTINGS_FLIPNOTE_PLAYER_VOLUME_DESCRIPTION"
msgstr "Ajusta el volumen del Reproductor de Flipnotes."

msgid "SETTINGS_FLIPNOTE_VIEW_FLIPNOTE_3D"
msgstr "Ver KWZs"

msgid "SETTINGS_FLIPNOTE_VIEW_FLIPNOTE_3D_DESCRIPTION"
msgstr "Al estar activado, se mostrarán los archivos KWZ de Flipnote Studio 3D. Hay ciertas funciones que podrían no funcionar en los archivos KWZ a diferencia de los archivos PPM, como los Filtros de Color y la Búsqueda."

msgid "SETTINGS_FLIPNOTE_VIEW_FLIPNOTE_3D_REFRESH"
msgstr "Para que esta opción surta efecto, debes actualizar la página."

msgid "SETTINGS_FLIPNOTE_VIEW_GALLERY"
msgstr "Modo Galería"

msgid "SETTINGS_FLIPNOTE_VIEW_GALLERY_DESCRIPTION"
msgstr "Solo se mostrarán las miniaturas de los Flipnotes mientras esté activado. Si el Modo Galería está activado, la opción Detalles Extra al Presionar Shift no funcionará."

msgid "SETTINGS_FLIPNOTE_VIEW_ORIGINAL_THUMBNAIL"
msgstr "Resolución Original de las Miniaturas"

msgid "SETTINGS_FLIPNOTE_VIEW_ORIGINAL_THUMBNAIL_DESCRIPTION"
msgstr "Al estar activado, se utilizarán las miniaturas incluídas en el archivo PPM. Usualmente las miniaturas originales son mucho menos coloridas y tienen una resolución más pequeña, por lo que se recomienda que mantengas esto desactivado."

msgid "SETTINGS_FLIPNOTE_VIEW_SORT_BY_FILENAME"
msgstr "Ordenar Flipnotes por Nombre de Archivo"

msgid "SETTINGS_FLIPNOTE_VIEW_SORT_BY_FILENAME_DESCRIPTION"
msgstr "Al estar activado, los Flipnotes serán ordenados utilizando el nombre de sus archivos. Se recomienda mantener esto desactivado para mantener el mismo orden de Flipnotes tanto en Flipnote Organizer como en Nintendo DSi."

msgid "SETTINGS_FLIPNOTE_VIEW_STICKERS"
msgstr "Mostrar Stickers en los Flipnotes"

msgid "SETTINGS_FLIPNOTE_VIEW_STICKERS_DESCRIPTION"
msgstr "Al estar activado, se mostrarán stickers por encima de las miniaturas. Se recomienda mantener esto activado para mantener el mismo orden de Flipnotes tanto en Flipnote Organizer como en Nintendo DSi."

msgid "SETTINGS_GALLERY_ICONS"
msgstr "Mostrar Iconos sobre Miniaturas en el Modo Galería"

msgid "SETTINGS_GALLERY_ICONS_DESCRIPTION"
msgstr "Mientras esto esté activado, se mostrarán íconos sobre las miniaturas de los Flipnotes al usar el Modo Galería. A menos que los íconos no te permitan ver las miniaturas, se recomienda mantener esto activado."

msgid "SETTINGS_GALLERY_THUMBNAIL_SCALE"
msgstr "Tamaño de Miniaturas en Modo Galería"

msgid "SETTINGS_GALLERY_THUMBNAIL_SCALE_DESCRIPTION"
msgstr "Ajusta el tamaño de las miniaturas en el Modo Galería."

msgid "SETTINGS_GAMEPADS"
msgstr "Mandos y Controles"

msgid "SETTINGS_GAMEPADS_DESCRIPTION"
msgstr "Utiliza mandos o controles para interactuar con Flipnote Organizer."

msgid "SETTINGS_JOYCON_PAIR"
msgstr "Pares de Joycon"

msgid "SETTINGS_JOYCON_PAIR_DESCRIPTION"
msgstr "Arrastra los Joycon conectados para formar pares. Si uno de los pares tiene un solo Joycon, deberás sostener el Joycon de lado."

msgid "SETTINGS_ORGANIZER_FIX_NAVBAR"
msgstr "Fix Navbar to the Top"

msgid "SETTINGS_ORGANIZER_FIX_NAVBAR_DESCRIPTION"
msgstr "The navigation bar will always be fixed to the top of the screen. This may be useful when you want to access settings without returning to the top of the page."

msgid "SETTINGS_PLAYER_COLOR_ACCESSIBILITY"
msgstr "Change Flipnote Player Colors"

msgid "SETTINGS_PLAYER_COLOR_ACCESSIBILITY_DESCRIPTION"
msgstr "Modifications to red and blue for those who have sensitivites to certain colors or tones, or color deficiencies. These options may make some Flipnotes look awkward as they weren't designed with variable color tones in mind."

msgid "SETTINGS_PLAYER_COLOR_MEMO_PLUS"
msgstr "Memo+ Enhancements"

msgid "SETTINGS_PLAYER_COLOR_MEMO_PLUS_DESCRIPTION"
msgstr "When enabled, the Flipnote Organizer will enable color enhancements for Flipnotes that support Memo+. It is recommended to keep this on."

msgid "SETTINGS_PLAYER_COLOR_MEMO_PLUS_LEARN_MORE"
msgstr "You can learn more about Memo+ at %s."

msgid "SETTINGS_PLAYER_COLOR_OPTION_COLORBLIND"
msgstr "Color Deficiency"

msgid "SETTINGS_PLAYER_COLOR_OPTION_DESATURATED"
msgstr "Desaturated"

msgid "SETTINGS_PLAYER_COLOR_OPTION_FLIPNOTE"
msgstr "Original"

msgid "SETTINGS_PLAYER_COLOR_OPTION_GRAYSCALE"
msgstr "Grayscale"

msgid "SETTINGS_PLAYER_COLOR_OPTION_PASTEL"
msgstr "Pastel"

msgid "SETTINGS_PLAYER_COLOR_OPTION_SOFT"
msgstr "Soft"

msgid "SETTINGS_PLAYER_INTERPOLATION"
msgstr "Flipnote Player Pixels Always Crisp"

msgid "SETTINGS_PLAYER_INTERPOLATION_DESCRIPTION"
msgstr "Pixels in the Flipnote Player will always be crisp at the cost of pixel distortion if using a scale between 1x and 2x or a non-standard zoom level."

msgid "SETTINGS_PLAYER_SCALE"
msgstr "Flipnote Player Scale"

msgid "SETTINGS_PLAYER_SCALE_DESCRIPTION"
msgstr "Adjust the scale of the Flipnote Player."

msgid "SETTINGS_PLAYER_TREBLE"
msgstr "Boost Flipnote Treble"

msgid "SETTINGS_PLAYER_TREBLE_DESCRIPTION"
msgstr "Boosts the volume of higher audio frequencies while playing Flipnotes."

msgid "SETTINGS_SHUFFLE_BUTTON"
msgstr "Shuffle Button"

msgid "SETTINGS_SHUFFLE_BUTTON_DESCRIPTION"
msgstr "If disabled, the shuffle button will be hidden and shuffle mode will not be available."

msgid "SETTINGS_THEME"
msgstr "Theme"

msgid "SETTINGS_THEME_DESCRIPTION"
msgstr "Set your preferred theme for the organizer."

msgid "SETTINGS_TITLE_ACCESSIBILITY"
msgstr "Accessibility"

msgid "SETTINGS_TITLE_ACCESSIBILITY_DESCRIPTION"
msgstr "Options intended to make usage more pleasant with changes to visuals, sound, etc."

# These settings are usually hidden, so don't worry about them too much.
msgid "SETTINGS_TITLE_DEVELOPER"
msgstr "Dev Settings"

msgid "SETTINGS_TITLE_DEVELOPER_DESCRIPTION"
msgstr "These features are still in their early phases and have a low likelihood of adoption."

msgid "SETTINGS_TITLE_EXPERIMENTAL"
msgstr "Experimental"

msgid "SETTINGS_TITLE_EXPERIMENTAL_DESCRIPTION"
msgstr "These features are in an unstable and experimental phase. They may be removed or break in the future."

msgid "SETTINGS_TITLE_GENERAL"
msgstr "General"

msgid "SETTINGS_TITLE_GENERAL_DESCRIPTION"
msgstr "General settings related to volume, sorting, how Flipnotes are listed, etc."

msgid "SETTINGS_TITLE_QUICK_SETTINGS"
msgstr "Quick Settings"

msgid "SETTINGS_TITLE_SETTINGS"
msgstr "Settings"

msgid "SETTINGS_USE_WIIMOTE"
msgstr "Use a Wiimote"

msgid "SETTINGS_USE_WIIMOTE_DESCRIPTION"
msgstr "Use a Wiimote to interact with the organizer one-handed, as well as get feedback such rumble. For information about using Wiimotes, visit %s"

msgid "SETTINGS_USE_WIIMOTE_DESCRIPTION_CALIBRATE"
msgstr "To recalibrate IR, try not to tilt your Wiimote too much and press A when one of your IR dots is within the boxes in each corner."

msgid "SETTINGS_VOLUME"
msgstr "Sound Effects Volume"

msgid "SETTINGS_VOLUME_DESCRIPTION"
msgstr "Adjust the volume of button sounds."

msgid "SETTINGS_WHISTLE_SOUND"
msgstr "Play Whistle Sound when Sorting"

msgid "SETTINGS_WHISTLE_SOUND_DESCRIPTION"
msgstr "When enabled, a whistle sound will play when you begin organizing Flipnotes. If you are sensitive to high-pitched noises, it is generally recommended to turn this off."

msgid "SETTINGS_WIIMOTE_CLASSIC_CONTROLLER_STICK_DEADZONE"
msgstr "Classic Controller Control Stick Deadzone"

msgid "SETTINGS_WIIMOTE_CLASSIC_CONTROLLER_STICK_DEADZONE_DESCRIPTION"
msgstr "Adjust the deadzone of the Classic Controller control sticks. Lower values may result in stick drift, while higher values may require you to tilt the sticks much farther."

msgid "SETTINGS_WIIMOTE_IN_QUICK_SETTINGS"
msgstr "Select Wiimote Button in Quick Settings"

msgid "SETTINGS_WIIMOTE_IN_QUICK_SETTINGS_DESCRIPTION"
msgstr "When enabled, a Select Wiimote button will be added to Quick Settings."

msgid "SETTINGS_WIIMOTE_IR_SENSITIVITY"
msgstr "Wiimote IR Camera Sensitivity"

msgid "SETTINGS_WIIMOTE_IR_SENSITIVITY_DESCRIPTION"
msgstr "Adjust the sensitivity of the Wiimote IR camera. Higher settings may cause additional dots to appear due to sunlight, smartphones, or heat sources."

msgid "SETTINGS_WIIMOTE_MEMORY_BACKUP"
msgstr "Backup Wiimote"

msgid "SETTINGS_WIIMOTE_NUNCHUK_STICK_DEADZONE"
msgstr "Nunchuk Control Stick Deadzone"

msgid "SETTINGS_WIIMOTE_NUNCHUK_STICK_DEADZONE_DESCRIPTION"
msgstr "Adjust the deadzone of the Nunchuk control stick. Lower values may result in stick drift, while higher values may require you to tilt the stick much farther."

msgid "SETTINGS_WIIMOTE_RUMBLE_FEEDBACK"
msgstr "Wiimote Rumble"

msgid "SETTINGS_WIIMOTE_RUMBLE_FEEDBACK_DESCRIPTION"
msgstr "When enabled, the Wiimote will rumble when interacting with certain things."

msgid "SETTINGS_WIIMOTE_SOUND_THROUGH_DEVICE_OUTPUT"
msgstr "Play Sounds Through TV When Wiimote Speaker is Muted"

msgid "SETTINGS_WIIMOTE_SOUND_THROUGH_DEVICE_OUTPUT_DESCRIPTION"
msgstr "When enabled, any sounds meant to be played from the Wiimote speaker will be played through your device's audio output if the Wiimote speaker is muted or cannot be used such as with RVL-CNT-01 Wiimotes."

msgid "SETTINGS_WIIMOTE_VOLUME"
msgstr "Wiimote Speaker Volume"

# RVL-CNT-01-TR is the device name when viewed in bluetooth and should not be changed.
msgid "SETTINGS_WIIMOTE_VOLUME_DESCRIPTION"
msgstr "Adjust the volume of the Wiimote speaker. Only RVL-CNT-01-TR Wiimotes support usage of the speaker."

